com.javagameengine.math

Class Quaternion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.javagameengine.math.Vector<Quaternion>
      • com.javagameengine.math.Quaternion

  • public class Quaternion
extends Vector<Quaternion>
    Quaternion vector utilizing floats. Replicates the capabilities of Vector4f in quaternion space. Provides a number of quaternion-specific methods for rotational operations.
